      • parseTintMode

        @Nullable
public static PorterDuff.Mode parseTintMode(int value,
                                                       @Nullable
                                                       PorterDuff.Mode defaultMode)
        Parses a PorterDuff.Mode from the specified value.
        Parameters:
        value - One of TINT_SRC_OVER, TINT_SRC_IN, TINT_SRC_ATOP, TINT_MULTIPLY, TINT_SCREEN, TINT_ADD.
        defaultMode - Default mode to return if the specified value flag has not been recognized.
